ay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Base: </strong>Improve & expand your raider's base to achieve powerful upgrades for your characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Raider Classes & Abilities:</strong> Unlock more races & upgrade your race abilities to deepen yourself further into the ruins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgradeable Weapons and Units:</strong> Craft your own equipment and level-up your raiders.</p></li></ul>",
